{"word":"G2660 - κατανύσσω - katanýssō - kat-an-oos'-so - Prick","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατανύσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katanýssō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-an-oos'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Prick</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - குத்தப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to prick, pierce; to pain the mind sharply, agitate it vehemently"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G3572 - νύσσω - nýssō - noos'-so/3572\">G3572</a>; to <i>pierce thoroughly</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>agitate</i> violently (&ldquo;sting to the quick&rdquo;): - prick.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2659/2659\">G2659</a>, <a href=\"#/G2660/2660\">G2660</a>"}]}